<div id="ctr"> <div id="hd"> <h1> Neuroscience For Kids </h1> </div>

<div id="mn"><h2>The Senses</h2>

<p>Many of these experiments and activities require children to be
blindfolded.  Remember that some people may not like to be blindfolded.  
In this case, have them cover their eyes with their hands.</p>

<table>
<tr><td>
<a href="chhearing.html"><img src="gif/manlistn.gif" alt="" /><br /> Hearing</a></td>

<td>
